      <b data-is-speakable>'War Doctor' David Nott: Treating COVID-19 Is Like Fighting An Invisible Enemy : Shots - Health News</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Trauma surgeon David Nott has volunteered in war zones and disaster areas around the world. Now he's treating COVID-19 patients in London. He calls the pandemic a "disaster zone for the whole world."</b>
